        {
          "scid": "sn56.71:1.1",
          "pli": "… “Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appakā te sattā ye pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā; atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā ye pāṇātipātā appaṭiviratā. ",
          "en": "“… the sentient beings who refrain from killing living creatures are few, while those who don’t refrain are many. …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.71:1.2",
          "pli": "Taṃ kissa hetu? … pe …. ",
          "en": " "
